Plugin

 - class -> path mapping

      home
      screensaver
      directory
      tracks (a list of tracks, such as Spotify playlist)
      album  (a list of tracks on the same album)
      albums (a list of albums)
      movies
      items
      images
      slideshow

 Which one is active is configurable somewhere and results in

  $ui.viewpath.home -> URL
  $ui.viewpath.screensaver -> URL

               


View manager for "directories"

 - Switchable by user between

   1 Load direct URL from page model
   2 Detect based on content  <- Each content type can have plugins
   3 Default list (directory) <- Can also be replaced

  url = selectview(
	   $page.model.glw.view,
           translate($page.contents, void, 
	             "album", $ui.viewpath.album ?? "theme://thedefault",
	             "albums", $ui.viewpath.albums ?? "theme://thedefault"),
           $ui.viewpath.directory ?? "theme://thedefault");





